# Go build artifacts
/bin/
/dist/
/coverage.out
/coverage.html
*.test
*.prof
*.coverprofile

# Local env/secrets
.env
.env.*
secrets/
private/
credentials/
*.pem
*.key

# Claude local/private
.claude/settings.local.json
CLAUDE.local.md

# /second-opinion skill: per-clone redaction patterns (not the .example template)
.claude/redact-patterns.txt
# /second-opinion skill: codex stderr / debug capture (gitignored — may contain
# code fragments and prompt content that should not enter git history)
.tdd/second-opinion-debug.log
# /second-opinion skill: per-cycle adjudication artifact (regenerated each cycle)
.tdd/second-opinion-completed.md
# require-second-opinion.sh enforcement audit log (local; contains paths only)
.tdd/second-opinion-enforcement.log
# Migration-script audit log (F12; local; contains paths + summary)
.tdd/migration-audit.log

# TDD per-cycle artifacts: gitignored. The active plan and red/green
# proofs reflect a specific in-flight cycle and would ship as stale
# active state to downstream consumers if committed. Templates at
# .tdd/templates/ are the authoritative shipped content; per-cycle
# files are local. (Pack-self bootstrap cycle 2026-05-08 finding.)
.tdd/current-plan.md
.tdd/red-proof.md
.tdd/green-proof.md
.tdd/codex/independent-design.md
.tdd/codex/disposition-matrix.md
.tdd/codex/round*.json
# v1.6.2: schema-context generator output (regenerated by the
# /second-opinion skill on every invocation if older than tdd-config.json)
.tdd/second-opinion/context/
# v1.7.0: per-cycle typed test-edit exception artifact + audit log
.tdd/exceptions/
.tdd/audit/
# v1.9.7: cycle-abandonment durable archive
.tdd/abandoned/
# v1.10.2: per-cycle session-resumption state + active pointer
.tdd/cycles/
.tdd/active

# v2.0/v2.1 runtime — runner lock + last-edit tag + Codex CLI capability
# probe cache. Regenerated on demand; never useful to track. Tripped the
# pre-tag-smoke gate during the v2.2.0 release; gitignoring so future
# releases don't have to stash.
.tdd/runner.lock
.tdd/.last-edit
.tdd/.codex-capabilities.json
.tdd/reviews/

# v2.2 ops-triage runtime — local classifier cache, observe log, session
# tags, pending-reason fallback, debt records, and the Codex preflight
# artifacts. All regenerated by the hooks. Never track these.
.tdd/ops-triage/
.tdd/ops-preflight/
.tdd/ops-debt/

# Adopter install backups created by setup scripts when they overwrite an
# existing .claude/settings.json. Local-only audit copies; never commit.
.claude/settings.json.bak-*

# Proposal-review artifacts (scripts/review/proposal-review.sh). One
# file per (proposal, SHA) run; local audit trail showing which Codex
# pass each proposal got before its slice 1 started. Same convention as
# .tdd/release/ for the pre-tag-smoke artifacts.
.tdd/review/

# OS / editor
.DS_Store
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*~
.tdd/second-opinion/reviews/
/.tdd/release/
